">Set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmySet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmySet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 返回 true</span>\nmySet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 返回 false</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> set1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string-property property\">'key1'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nset1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nset1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// 返回 true</span>\nset1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string-property property\">'key1'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 会返回 false，因为其是另一个对象的引用</span>\nset1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string-property property\">'key1'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 现在 set1 中有 2 条（不同引用的）对象了</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"使用 has 方法"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-set.prototype.has\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Set.prototype.has</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Set.has","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Ref